        "title": "feat: group model select with collapsible panel in Control UI",
        "body": "Adds a custom model select panel that replaces the native `<select>` with grouped, collapsible options organized by model family.\r\n\r\n**Features:**\r\n- Models grouped by family: DeepSeek, GPT, Claude, GLM, Gemini, Qwen, Kimi, etc.\r\n- Collapsible group headers with toggle arrow\r\n- Expand/collapse all button in the default model row\r\n- Unknown model families auto-create new groups\r\n- Full dark/light theme support via CSS variables\r\n- Visual height/font consistency with adjacent native controls\r\n- SVG chevronDown icons matching agent select style\r\n- Default model option pinned at top outside any group\r\n\r\n**File changed:** `ui/src/ui/chat/session-controls.ts`",
